IB/core: Improve ib_map_mr_sg() documentation

Document that ib_map_mr_sg() is able to map physically discontiguous
sg-lists as a single MR. Change IB_MR_TYPE_SG_GAPS_REG into
IB_MR_TYPE_SG_GAPS.

